{"tid":2122653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"青山病人陳云又轉方向，反證熱狗投共","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T00:19:05.000Z","uid":137704,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6c90486ba05b46a7941b6e9d1bb39530d64388","tid":2122653,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:23:15.000Z","msg":"青山病人陳云: <span class=\"red\">口罩是新冷戰的反共象徵物</span>！龐佩奧在今晨的演講中，特別談到口罩。他說中國隱瞞瘟疫，連累他們要戴口罩！這是特朗普總統在日前忽然在公開場合全隊人戴口罩的政治玄機！（之前之後他都無戴口罩）<br />\n<span class=\"red\">在西方，戴口罩是埋怨中國、仇恨中國散播疫病的外在行為。口罩是新冷戰的象徵物！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqOktPy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqOktPy.png&h=7b8b3167&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n即係話熱狗唔戴口罩係投共!<br />\n點解有陳云風火輪哩樣野，買哂咁多邊實會中。三月話疫情就完、疫情是假的，完左未?<br />\n老師又中! 中風就有你份。"},{"pid":"b79324ef9b0611fb5f3e7aff4d9fa8ffbfb9cb5c","tid":2122653,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"佩清 巡邏時夠無戴口罩，又投共咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0317faf0f64581dab0c235e0fc6b9fd066f5941c","tid":2122653,"uid":191790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"咁特朗普之前唔戴口罩係咪投共"},{"pid":"9698055ff4747608117088ac5cba673ff5dde8da","tid":2122653,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"如果陳雲為咗政治上嘅反共而呼籲戴口罩係咪對真理嘅背叛？"},{"pid":"4b197704b203f6817059ae2688e6c156021194fb","tid":2122653,"uid":123926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"而家又唔係鳩戴口罩喇?"},{"pid":"9abbc65314bc25764b2a8ec061a8d37602b80b05","tid":2122653,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"龐佩奧特別談到口罩，他說中國隱瞞瘟疫，令他們要戴口罩。在西方，戴口罩是埋怨中國、仇恨中國散播疫病的外在行為。現在我終於明白，為何香港特區政府要制定口罩強制令，因為要反華反共！因為健康人戴口罩根本毫無保護作用，而且帶來的感染弊病更多。<br />\n所有在香港投資的、居住的，都必須認識清楚世界大局的突變。戴口罩是逃避現實的懦夫鴕鳥行為，而且帶有仇恨中國的反華意思！香港政府記得要加強要香港人戴口罩啊！"},{"pid":"64c15074a0bcb73a1024a01e7f6674c98af6f1f0","tid":2122653,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"又，陳雲一貫立場係全民戴口罩無意義 有冇變過？"},{"pid":"694a9a7b77219f7b8b971966fd100afe95e761b6","tid":2122653,"uid":233643,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"語境都唔識睇 定唔知為反而反啦<br />\n如果係前者你都幾撚悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a213d4c96bc47bca4bfdc845523de47039563c","tid":2122653,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:31:16.000Z","msg":"老屍又中啊！！！！！！！～～～～～～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50736a8d5ec4f6a61b60af4d63a2e67007036f8b","tid":2122653,"uid":153496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"泛民港獨配合香港政府反共？<br />\n咁應該反共定投共啊？<br />\n口罩係反共象徵咁又啫係戴唔戴好啫？<br />\n買兩邊買到唔知邊邊打邊邊<br />\n想點啊陳老師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a9008e4b727bb3d2f44a85e7847c607c254f80","tid":2122653,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"應該呢排入左啲淘寶口罩要散貨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11f597a416aa6f334ca9138f4938ebfafad1ec5","tid":2122653,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"老師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ee037d98931151250dbe3df003cda5552b1ef5","tid":2122653,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"國屍又中，中中中又中"},{"pid":"af981af8d030cdd2dca7599124ab7c666e09f792